Fy_Cortex
This is my map submission for the mapping contest. It contains a custom skybox, made by myself, background music from HL2 and a wierd yet awsome effect in the 3D skybox that has to be seen to be appreciated. The map is quite small for lighting gameplay, and each player starts with an M4 with 300 ammo. Enjoy! and don't forget to vote me the winner! =D
